Gunmen, in Ondo State, kidnapped a four-year-old girl, Esther Olisa, in Danjuma axis of Akure, Akure South Local Government. The police disclosed that the kidnapper has been arrested.
The Public Relations Officer of the Ondo State Police Command, Fumilayo Odunlami, disclosed that one suspect had been arrested by the police over the kidnapping of the child.
The police disclosed that the girl child was kidnapped at their residence last Saturday after dinner with the family.
Meanwhile, Amatekun operatives are yet to respond to the kidnap in the state.
